        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR5c0057-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-16T03:33:41.529+09:00">道產生作為同一體的原始混沌之氣，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-16T03:34:23.876+09:00">這統一體又分裂為陰陽這兩個對立面，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-16T03:35:28.671+09:00">這兩個對立面又產生新的第三者（陰陽和合），</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-16T03:36:34.174+09:00">新生的第三者產生千差萬別的東西（萬物）。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-16T04:25:41.177+09:00">萬物各自包涵陰陽兩個對立面，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-16T04:26:39.282+09:00">這陰陽兩氣，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_042-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-01-16T04:28:19.829+09:00">互相激蕩而得道統一。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:14:50.79+09:00">“道"，说得出，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:14:55.416+09:00">它就不是永恒的道；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:15:05.275+09:00">''名"，叫得出，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:15:15.209+09:00">它就不是永恒 的名。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:15:23.097+09:00">“无”，用以称述天地之始原，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.8" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:15:26.694+09:00">“有”，用以称述万物之根本。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.9" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:16:05.785+09:00">所以，应该从万物永恒的原始状态中去观察“道"的微妙，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.10" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:16:14.709+09:00">应该从万物不 变的根本之处去观察“道"的显豁。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.11" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:16:22.429+09:00">此两者（上文讲的"有"“无”）同出 一源而名称互异，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.12" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:16:29.551+09:00">它们都称得上是深远莫测的，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.13" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:16:34.548+09:00">从有形的深远境界到 达无形的深远境界，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR5c0057_tls_001-1a.14" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-05-18T02:16:35.385+09:00">这就是通向一切奥妙神秘的总门径。</seg>
                </p>
